    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/c524126cc9df674d3c5047751836ff2b.poster.avif?t=1679366893\" width=362 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/c524126cc9df674d3c5047751836ff2b.webm?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/c524126cc9df674d3c5047751836ff2b.mp4?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>QQ交流群:484680319<br>B站账号：末日幸存者官方账号<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/d1c1f40780502f80c889df593f45e7e2.avif?t=1679366893\" width=450 height=95 /></span><br>《DOOMSDAY SURVIVORS》是一款末日生存题材的rogue弹幕射击游戏。在末日荒芜的土地上，使用多个能力迥异的角色，随机选择各式各样的武器搭配来进化更强的超武，抵御一波又一波生化怪物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/f9353b3323090546ddd012184df40ece.poster.avif?t=1679366893\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/f9353b3323090546ddd012184df40ece.webm?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/f9353b3323090546ddd012184df40ece.mp4?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/965c7433645e6fa0a873cdf4423ea35b.poster.avif?t=1679366893\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/965c7433645e6fa0a873cdf4423ea35b.webm?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/965c7433645e6fa0a873cdf4423ea35b.mp4?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/fcb935ba0b0480430fb4bb3ad4326478.avif?t=1679366893\" width=450 height=95 /></span><br>拥有各式各样的武器，其中天师符、金箍棒、火焰枪、电磁枪、重机枪、等等，尝试多种多样的组合，使用不同的搭配来发挥最强的能力！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/a996ca34eb8396a91bde4caaf758ada2.poster.avif?t=1679366893\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/a996ca34eb8396a91bde4caaf758ada2.webm?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/a996ca34eb8396a91bde4caaf758ada2.mp4?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/cb0b73b35dc647b8e6be61f143f7bf00.poster.avif?t=1679366893\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/cb0b73b35dc647b8e6be61f143f7bf00.webm?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285520/extras/cb0b73b35dc647b8e6be61f143f7bf00.mp4?t=1679366893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>能力迥异的角色，不同的角色带有不同的能力！",
